Package genetic_algorithm.population

Class Population

java.lang.Object
genetic_algorithm.population.Population
public class Population
extends java.lang.Object
This is the SINGLETON class. As every class in the project should work on the same population class,thats why it employs singleton instance. (i.e.,) it has only one instance to work on the same data throughout the project. I have implemented thread safe lazy initialization using wrapperClass because I want to have the Population instance to be created only if the Genetic Algorithm Runner class starts running (i.e.,) only when the application starts running
Author:
AISHWARYA SUKALE,20251514:
